{"tid":2000681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一本屬於手足嘅攝影集要人！！！","createTime":"2020-05-04T04:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T12:38:50.000Z","uid":3513,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af886ed8a78b768487051bd95267ae36b1a49598","tid":2000681,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:37:44.000Z","msg":"二零二零年六月，抗爭運動將走到第一個年頭。The Locals現計劃於六月聯同八位本土獨立攝影師出版獨立攝影集（中英雙語）。攝影集將集合攝影師們在抗爭運動期間所拍攝的影像，以相集的形式展示和聯繫八種不同的視野，將香港人過去一年的經歷製成攝影集，將歷史流傳下去。<br />\n<br />\n此外，The Locals亦希望將攝影集發行到外國，藉此引起更多國際關注，同時盼用相片，將真相傳遞給更多渴望民主自由的人，要牢牢堅守信念直至黎明來到一刻。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">相片會印證歷史；歷史會還我們公道。</span><br />\n<br />\n銷售目標：10,000本；收益扣除成本、加印儲備及攝影師補貼後，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至少會有港幣40萬能夠捐到黃國桐律師所發起的「保護傘」計劃並直接支援流亡台灣的香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/thelocals852/the-year-of-the-awakened\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fthelocals852%2Fthe-year-of-the-awakened&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=37e16de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/thelocals852/the-year-of-the-awakened</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_HHOAIAiYE/?igshid=1bezz9t43uyaq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_HHOAIAiYE%2F%3Figshid%3D1bezz9t43uyaq&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=14b54a34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_HHOAIAiYE%2F%3Figshid%3D1bezz9t43uyaq&h=2dfd1a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B_HHOAIAiYE/?igshid=1bezz9t43uyaq</a>"},{"pid":"25101562a914984a51a61ffbf154796c835f2b2f","tid":2000681,"uid":28818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://